\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 12, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104fcg1703059864210.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fcg1703059864210.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/fcg1703059864210.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"smc1665702782435\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"smc1665702782435__displaylength_216180\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the display length of a <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> when displayed in the system character set.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"smc1665702782435__topic_d71180e1_d71181e1_d71182e1\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"smc1665702782435__note_n1z_qx2_vzb\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">displaylength</code> statement is deprecated. It\n            has been superseded by<code class=\"ph codeph\"> $displaylength</code> function, which is applicable to\n            all component types.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smc1665702782435__p_d71183e1_d71184e1_d71185e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">displaylength</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smc1665702782435__p_d71186e1_d71187e1_d71188e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">displaylength vString</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"smc1665702782435__topic_d46787e1_d46788e1_d46789e1_d46790e1_d46791e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d738268e86\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smc1665702782435__p_d71192e1_d71193e1_d71194e1\">Setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> has no effect on subsequent processing.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smc1665702782435__p_d71195e1_d71196e1_d71197e1\">Setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span> returns the length of <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> when displayed in the system character set. The length is expressed in bytes.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"smc1665702782435__topic_d46792e1_d46793e1_d46794e1_d46795e1_d46796e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d738268e107\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"smc1665702782435__d6114e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tec1665703247413.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$SYS_CHARSET</a><p>Specify the character set used for communication with the operating system and for communication between Uniface and non-Uniface components, if they are not Unicode-based.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mmv1665703007311.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$displaylength</a><p>Return the display length of a String when displayed in the system character set.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5563117\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5563117\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "displaylength (deprecated) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 12, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the display length of a String when displayed in the system character set. Note: The displaylength statement is deprecated. It has been superseded by $displaylength function, which is applicable to all component types. displaylength String Example: displaylength vString Return Values Setting $status has no effect on subsequent processing. Setting $result returns the length of String when displayed in the system character set. The length is expressed in bytes. Use Allowed in all component types. Related Links $SYS_CHARSET Specify the character set used for communication with the operating system and for communication between Uniface and non-Uniface components, if they are not Unicode-based. $displaylength Return the display length of a String when displayed in the system character set. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}